getMainCategory

public SKCategories.SKPOIMainCategory getMainCategory()
Returns the main category. It's available only for POI's. It describes what main category the POI belongs to. While there are hundreds of categories, only few main categories are defined , for clearer categorization. See SKCategories.SKPOIMainCategory.

Returns:
main category.
